{"tid":2315283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"fb加劇掃「黃」 留言抗爭即停權","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T09:16:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f33458f83b433086c8051a5fb184be2a716d194","tid":2315283,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201207/LEWEXELQ6ND77PTYQCDIYLLG74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201207%2FLEWEXELQ6ND77PTYQCDIYLLG74%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=8c6061be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201207%2FLEWEXELQ6ND77PTYQCDIYLLG74%2F&h=f2f56e86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201207/LEWEXELQ6ND77PTYQCDIYLLG74/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nfb加劇掃「黃」 留言抗爭即停權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-H_u4d50ZvnsVnjdh9wj5sgNrhI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7ALZWQLW3FASRNQ5TZJMV4XYOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-H_u4d50ZvnsVnjdh9wj5sgNrhI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7ALZWQLW3FASRNQ5TZJMV4XYOY.jpg&h=85b9a31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■店主Brian（左）及雪瑤（右）的IG專頁被指違反社群守則，廣告賬號被停權。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港社交網絡噤聲風波越演越烈。多名網絡「被消失」人士向本報指控facebook掃「黃」日益加劇，無聲打壓曝光率、自定禁語，更將賬號停權；又直斥上訴機制形同虛設。有學者分析指美國大選期間，平台將審查用戶的人工智能上調得異常敏感，「有殺錯無放過」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網店遭禁賣廣告限曝光<br />\n<br />\n去年8月Brian與雪瑤的網店開業，其後藉「<a href=\"http://Uclopia.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUclopia.hk&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=28468ade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Uclopia.hk</a>」名義吸納逾兩萬人追蹤其Instagram專頁，一直有分享反極權文宣。<a href=\"http://今年9月Uclopia.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88Uclopia.hk&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=eedd388f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">今年9月Uclopia.hk</a>在本報Instagram專頁一篇警方凌駕證監會查操縱壹傳媒股價的報道下，留言「又趕住衝出嚟X」後，即被噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n店主Brian指翌日獲facebook通知留言違反《社群守則》及《廣告刊登政策》，其廣告賬戶已遭停用，意味網店無緣再賣廣告。其後他再獲通知，<a href=\"http://與廣告賬戶一同登記的Uclopia.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%88%87%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8C%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E7%9A%84Uclopia.hk&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7219f35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">與廣告賬戶一同登記的Uclopia.hk</a>的Instagram專頁也因違規被限制曝光率，最多僅能接觸千人，永久生效。Brian向facebook上訴，惟只獲回覆指停權已是最終決定。最終兩人要以虛擬私人網絡（VPN）和舊電郵才暫時瞞過狙擊，在社交平台上取得「新身份」。<br />\n<br />\n有逾十萬人讚好的專頁一樣難逃「清洗」。藝人阮民安去年起在專頁積極表態，今年兩度遭停權。他指年內收到六次警告，上月3日因發文支持總統特朗普連任再遭停權。<br />\n<br />\n本報向facebook查詢，僅獲回覆指已制訂社群守則列出允許或禁止的行為。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"80d7f5802c48f384ab75133886ac2a95d0157675","tid":2315283,"uid":18999,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">MEWE</span></span>"},{"pid":"e72d923bed2723973944626c9cf316ba8f49778f","tid":2315283,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"MEWE"},{"pid":"fc8ae6f614dc0ffefe6c46d83b9361f038b02c1e","tid":2315283,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"MEWE"},{"pid":"2f76b7142de105018b697f84566a95647436662e","tid":2315283,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"MEWE<br />\nfb驚唔夠多人去，幫下手趕"},{"pid":"1efa8289d59fbee156fc90e018f15a9570ed7543","tid":2315283,"uid":371606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"MeWe<br />\nFB請咁多中國人做審查<br />\n梗係無用啦！<br />\nFB係中國的"}]}